You will be using Github to collaborate with your team during the class and submit your assignments
Everyone should have an account
1 repo per group
Share your Github repo with us: you will submit your code through Github 
Assignment: test Github features
Create a repo for your group - set it to private and name it “albert-hod-101-2026-your-group-number”
Add all group members to collaborate
Add us to your repo (regisamichiafox, woodwoodpan)
Individually:
Create a branch with your name and commit changes to your branch by creating a new file with one line
Open a pull request, and ask another team member for review
Other team member: Make a comment and ask for changes (eg adding a word in the file)
Make the requested change
Other team member: Check the changes and validate PR if OK
Merge PR into the main branch when it is validated
